{"ID":270301, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"301\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs300.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs302.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 301<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">the power and authority of the Holy Priesthood,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> they will cease to increase when they die;<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> that is,\n  they will not have any children after the resurrection. But those who are married by the power and\n  authority of the priesthood in this life, and continue without committing the sin against the Holy\n  Ghost,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> will continue to increase and have children in the celestial glory.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> The unpardonable sin is\n  to shed innocent blood,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> or be accessory thereto. All other sins will be visited with judgment in the\n  flesh, and the spirit being delivered to the buffetings of Satan<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> until the day of the Lord Jesus.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The way I know in whom to confide&mdash;God tells me in whom I may place confidence.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Celestial Glory<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">In the celestial glory there are three heavens or degrees; and in order to obtain the highest, a\n  man must enter into this order of the priesthood [meaning the new and everlasting covenant of\n  marriage]; and if he does not, he cannot obtain it. He may enter into the other, but that is the end of\n  his kingdom: he cannot have an increase.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> (May 16, 1843.) DHC 5:391-392.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Salvation and Sure Word of Prophecy<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Salvation means a man&rsquo;s being placed beyond the power of all his enemies.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The more sure word of prophecy<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> means a man&rsquo;s knowing that he is sealed up unto eternal\n  life<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> by revelation and the spirit of prophecy,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> through the power of the holy priesthood.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> It is\n  impossible for a man to be saved in ignorance.<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Paul saw the third heavens,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> and I more.<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> Peter penned the most sublime language of any of the\n  apostles. (May 17, 1843.) DHC 5:392.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">God Breathed into Adam His Spirit<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The 7th verse of 2nd chapter of Genesis ought to read&mdash;God breathed into Adam his spirit [i.e.,\n  Adam&rsquo;s spirit] or breath of life;<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> but when the word &ldquo;ruach&rdquo; applies to Eve, it should be translated\n  lives.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Eternal Duration of Matter<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Speaking of eternal duration of matter, I said:<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">There is no such thing as immaterial matter. All spirit is<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116361\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116361)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116361)\">D&amp;C 132:18-21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116287\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116287)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116287)\">D&amp;C 131:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116352\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116352)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116352)\">D&amp;C 132:16-17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112247\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112247)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112247)\">Alma 39:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116367\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116367)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116367)\">D&amp;C 132:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116397\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116397)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116397)\">D&amp;C 132:26-27<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109464\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109464)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109464)\">1 Cor. 5:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116394\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116394)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116394)\">D&amp;C 132:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109630\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109630)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109630)\">2 Cor. 1:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113198\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113198)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113198)\">D&amp;C 10:37<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116280\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116280)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116280)\">D&amp;C 131:1-4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106715\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106715)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106715)\">Ps. 44:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108421\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108421)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108421)\">Luke 1:71<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116079\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116079)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116079)\">D&amp;C 127:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110534\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110534)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110534)\">2 Pet. 1:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114304\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114304)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114304)\">D&amp;C 68:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111398\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111398)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111398)\">Jacob 4:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111863\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111863)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111863)\">Alma 9:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113217\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113217)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113217)\">D&amp;C 11:25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114642\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114642)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114642)\">D&amp;C 84:19-24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116302\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116302)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116302)\">D&amp;C 131:5-6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109693\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109693)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109693)\">2 Cor. 12:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114372\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114372)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114372)\">D&amp;C 76:1-119<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116611\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116611)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116611)\">D&amp;C 137:1-10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"105966\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 105966)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(105966)\">Gen. 2:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}